/-!
# Congruence subgroups (deprecated local copy)

This file previously contained a local copy of definitions for congruence subgroups of
`SL(2, ℤ)` such as `Γ(N)`, `Γ₀(N)` and `Γ₁(N)`. These have since been upstreamed to mathlib;
use `Mathlib.NumberTheory.ModularForms.CongruenceSubgroups` instead.

The file is retained as an empty placeholder to preserve the import path.
-/
